Invocation Name: w. k. s. u.
des:
Play live radio from any of WKSU's program streams.

 "Alexa, play WKSU”

 "Alexa, ask WKSU to play Folk Alley”

 "Alexa, ask WKSU to play classical"

 "Alexa, ask WKSU to play news"

To stop playing, say "Alexa, stop"

Find out what program or song is playing.

 "Alexa, ask WKSU what's playing" 

 "Alexa, ask WKSU what's playing on Folk Alley"

 "Alexa, ask WKSU what's playing on classical"

 "Alexa, ask WKSU what's playing on news"

Optionally link this skill to your WKSU Member Portal account to to access the fund-drive-free stream or to find out about your membership status.
